        @NotNull
T dateOrBefore(@NotNull

        Searches first Revision which was created before or exactly at date.
        Returns:
        found Revision or baseline revision if found revision was less then baseline revision.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if repository(String) method called before this method, because there is no implementation for revision search according to specified repositories.

      • dateOrAfter

        @NotNull
T dateOrAfter(@NotNull
                       java.util.Date date)
        Searches first Revision which was created after or exactly at date.
        Returns:
        founded Revision or undefined Revision if no revisions were found according to date.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if repository(String) method called before this method, because there is no implementation for revision search according to specified repositories.
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if this RevisionSelector instance is already in finished state.
        Since:
        3.9.3
